es;\r\n mso-style-priority:99;\r\n mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\r\n mso-para-margin-top:0in;\r\n mso-para-margin-right:0in;\r\n mso-para-margin-bottom:10.0pt;\r\n mso-para-margin-left:0in;\r\n line-height:115%;\r\n mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n font-size:11.0pt;\r\n font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;\r\n mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\n mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\n mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\n mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n mso-ansi-language:IN;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;![endif]--&gt;\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed align=\"center\"><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>PENILAIAN/REVIEW\r\nTEKNIS TIM EDITORIAL UGM PRESS</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><i xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></i></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Judul\r\nnaskah<span xss=removed> </span>:<i xss=removed> Pesona Candi Jogja</i></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Penulis<span xss=removed> </span>: M. Zainul\r\nArifin</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>Penilaian</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>1. Judul apakah menarik?</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Judul cukup menarik, cukup menggambarkan isi naskah. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>2. Proporsionalitas jumlah\r\nhalaman?</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Jumlah halaman naskah secara keseluruhan adalah 198 halaman yang lebih\r\ndidominasi oleh gambar-gambar. Pembagian pembahasan mengenai candi Hindu dan\r\nBuddha cukup proporsional. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>3. Kesesuaian sitasi antara\r\nuraian dan daftar pustaka?</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Meskipun lebih didominasi oleh gambar-gambar,\r\nnaskah masih menyajikan uraian penjelasan. Sayangnya, banyak pernyataan-pernyataan\r\ndan informasi yang diberikan penulis tidak diikuti dengan penulisan sumbernya.\r\nDi bagian belakang terdapat Bibliography yang membuat 19 sumber pustaka. Namun,\r\ntidak ada satu pun yang dituliskan di dalam naskah. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Sumber disertasi Mundardjito (2002) tidak ada di\r\nBibliography.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>4. Sistematika penyajian/format\r\nnaskah? </span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Tampaknya, naskah ini ditulis untuk keperluan\r\npromosi pariwisata. Dilihat dari sistematikanya, naskah dibagi menjadi 2\r\nbagian, bagian yang membahas candi-candi bercorak Hindu kemudian diikuti dengan\r\npembahasan candi-candi bercorak Buddha yang semuanya ada di Yogyakarta. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Penyajiannya\r\nberupa narasi mengenai arsitektur candi, sejarah penemuannya, lokasi, dan disertai\r\ndengan foto/gambar candi-candi tersebut</span><span xss=removed>. Hanya paparan, tanpa analisis\r\nkritis. Setiap pernyataan dan data penemuan yang diungkapkan di dalam naskah tidak\r\ndisertai dengan penulisan sumbernya (meskipun di belakang terdapat\r\nBibliography). Hal ini menjadikan naskah ini berisiko terindikasi plagiarisme. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><i xss=removed><span xss=removed>Its\r\nbased off of analysis of the ceramic; chinaware (pottery) fragment can be known\r\nthat pottery fragment came from the place forms of difference pottery. They are\r\njug, bowl, urn, cover of the crock and stove.</span></i><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Banyak kutipan-kutipan yang menyebutkan bahwa hasil ekskavasi di candi\r\ntertentu ditemukan keramik dari Cina. Namun, tidak ada satu pun gambar foto yang\r\nmenunjukkan penemuan keramik tersebut. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Dalam satu halaman, selain terdapat nama penulis\r\nsendiri (M. Zainul Arifin), juga tercantum nama-nama lain seperti M. Anas\r\nHastian, Dwi Cahyo Nugroho, Nidlol, Ahshonuddin Atabik, Taufik Hidayat, dan Husnul\r\nKotimah. Akan tetapi, di bagian sampul dan narasi penulis hanya tercantum nama M.\r\nZainul Arifin. Apakah nama-nama tersebut juga berkontribusi dalam penulisan\r\nnaskah? Jika iya, maka harus juga dituliskan dalam sampul dan dimasukkan ke\r\ndalam Tentang Penulis. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>5. Sumber gambar dan tabel?</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Sesuai dengan judulnya, tak heran jika naskah ini\r\nmenyertakan gambar foto candi sebagai penunjang. Namun, gambar yang disertakan\r\ntidak disertai catatan sumbernya. Tidak diketahui apakah gambar-gambar tersebut\r\nmerupakan dokumentasi pribadi penulis atau penulis mengambil dari sumber lain. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Tidak ada tabel dalam naskah. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>6. Kualitas gambar dan tabel?</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Kualitas gambar foto yang disertakan sangat baik.\r\nGambar tidak pecah. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Tidak ada tabel di dalam naskah. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>7. Kebahasaan (unsur\r\nplagiarisme, bahasa/kalimat yang masih kacau)?</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Meskipun diberi judul berbahasa Indonesia, isi\r\nnaskah ditulis dalam bahasa Inggris. Perlu diperjelas lagi siapa target pembaca\r\nnaskah ini nantinya. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Bahasa Inggris yang digunakan terlihat masih kental\r\nmenggunakan struktur kalimat bahasa Indonesia. Kalimat-kalimatnya masih\r\nberputar-putar sehingga membingungkan. Topik-topik pembahasannya juga tidak\r\ndituangkan dengan teratur dan kronologis. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Contoh: </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Sambisari\r\ntemple lies in Sambisari hamlet, Purwomartani Village, Kalasan sub-District,\r\nSleman Regency Yogyakara, Indonesia. Sambi sari temple found by a farmer that\r\nwas working on land that belongs to Karyowinangun while his hoe hit the carved\r\nstone which was part of the ruins temple. The news of discovery reached the\r\narcheology office in Prambanan. The excavation and reconstruction works was\r\ncompleted in March 1987 <u>It was discovered by a peasant who was digging up\r\nhis field in 1966.</u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Ditemukan banyak kalimat yang tidak memenuhi\r\nstruktur sebuah kalimat lengkap S + P (+ O + K). Dibutuhkan penyuntingan secara\r\nmenyeluruh untuk memperbaikinya. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Contoh: </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>The temple remains were inundated by a 6.5 meters layer of lahar from\r\n<u>Merapi Mount the general outline of</u> the temple quarters is similar to\r\nthat of Prambanan Temple, but in a more modest scale.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Based on the research it was known that this statue was part of a\r\nbuilding from the excavation, the ruins of a building consisting of the top, a\r\npart of body and base of a temple, was found furthermore trial reconstruction\r\nwas conducted to the findings, though there was lot of new stone on the body\r\nthe restoration of the Gebang Temple was carried out in 1937 to 1939, led by\r\nProf. Dr. Ir.V.R. Van Romondt.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>-<span xss=removed>\r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Penggunaan tanda baca yang buruk. Penulis tampaknya\r\nkurang memperhatikan penggunaan dan fungsi tanda baca sehingga apa yang ingin\r\ndisampaikan menjadi tidak dapat dipahami, mana bagian yang harus diberi tanda\r\ntitik untuk mengakhiri kalimat, mana yang harus diberi tanda koma. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Contoh: </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>An inscribed gold plate found among the ruins was dated early to\r\nmid-9th century, bit most the structures visible show resemblances with Candi\r\nPrambanan<u>. W</u>hich seem to point to the second half of the 9th <u>century\r\nCandi Ijo</u> is a terraced sanctuary composed of many buildings, including\r\ntemples and stone platforms.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>8. Tema apakah menarik?</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed>Naskah buku ini lebih ditujukan untuk keperluan promosi pariwisata.\r\nMeski temanya cukup menarik karena berupaya mendokumentasikan candi-candi yang\r\nada di Yogyakarta, namun tidak sesuai dengan target pasar penerbit.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>9. Kesimpulan</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><s><span xss=removed>Dapat terbit</span></s><span xss=removed> / belum dapat terbit</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed align=\"right\"><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed align=\"right\"><span xss=removed>Yogyakarta, 24 Juli 2019</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed align=\"right\"><span xss=removed>Tim Evaluasi Naskah UGM Press</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" xss=removed><span xss=removed></span></p>\r\n\r\n', 'dwiratna', '2019-07-25 07:33:17', '2019-07-29 00:00:00', '2019-07-24 00:00:00', '2'),
